text: Oktyabrskoye () is a rural locality (a village) in Tavtimanovsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 164 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 24 km from Iglino, 6 km from Tavtimanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Oktyabrskoye, Iglinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
